== 迴響 ==

=== 專業評價 ===

本片獲得多數影評人的讚美。根據影評[[汇总媒体|匯總]]網站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]上收集的283份評論文章，其中有261份給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為92%，平均得分8.10（最高10分），該網站的共識評價寫道：「《人造意識》注重想法更勝於特效，不過仍是視覺觀感精美、不常見的迷人科幻電影。」<ref>{{Cite web |title=Ex Machina |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ex_machina |access-date=2022-06-09 |work=Rotten Tomatoes |language=en |archive-date=2022-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516215813/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ex_machina }}</ref>另一網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上收集的42篇評論中則有36篇好評，無差評，6篇褒貶不一，綜合評分78（最高100），屬好評居多<ref>{{Cite web |title=Ex Machina |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/ex-machina |access-date=2022-06-09 |work=Metacritic |language=en |archive-date=2015-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150410214306/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/ex-machina }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===

在英國，本片於首映週末（1月23日－25日）在442間電影院放映，票房贏過同期上映的《[[神鬼大盜|神鬼大盜]]》和《{{tsl|en|The Gambler (2014 film)|玩命賭徒}}》，共進帳109萬英鎊，排名該週末第五<ref>{{Cite web |last=Gant |first=Charles |date=2015-01-28 |title=American Sniper's adjective no obstacle as it outguns UK competition again |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/jan/28/uk-box-office-american-sniper-ex-machina-beyond-clueless |website=The Guardian |language=en |access-date=2022-06-17 |archive-date=2022-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220615112930/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/jan/28/uk-box-office-american-sniper-ex-machina-beyond-clueless }}</ref>。第二個週末（1月30日－2月1日），本片賺進41萬英鎊，排名第八<ref>{{Cite web |last=Gant |first=Charles |date=2015-02-03 |title=Big Hero 6 proves a Marvel as Kingsman spies the runner-up spot at UK box office |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2015/feb/03/big-hero-6-marvel-pips-kingsman-at-uk-box-office |website=The Guardian |language=en |access-date=2022-06-17 |archive-date=2021-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211201113159/https://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2015/feb/03/big-hero-6-marvel-pips-kingsman-at-uk-box-office }}</ref>。美國方面，本片先採取[[有限上映|有限上映]]模式，共有四間電影院在首映週末放映本片，票房約為25萬美元<ref>{{Cite web |last=Subers |first=Ray |date=2015-04-12 |title=Weekend Report: 'Furious 7' Repeats, Sets Opening Day Record in China |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/article/ed813630468/ |website=Box Office Mojo |access-date=2022-06-17 |language=en |archive-date=2021-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210518135030/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/article/ed813630468/ }}</ref>，排名第18<ref>{{Cite web |title=Domestic 2015 Weekend 15 |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/2015W15/ |website=Box Office Mojo |access-date=2022-06-17 |language=en |archive-date=2022-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220114021809/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/2015W15/ }}</ref>。隔週末，A24將上映影院加開到39間，進帳約81.4萬美元<ref>{{Cite web |last=Subers |first=Ray |date=2015-04-19 |title=Weekend Report: 'Furious 7' Beats 'Blart,' Passes $1.1 Billion Worldwide |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/article/ed1065288708/ |website=Box Office Mojo |access-date=2022-06-17 |language=en |archive-date=2022-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220408044834/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/article/ed1065288708/ }}</ref>，名列第15<ref>{{Cite web |title=Domestic 2015 Weekend 16 |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/2015W16/ |website=Box Office Mojo |access-date=2022-06-17 |language=en |archive-date=2022-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220114021531/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/2015W16/ }}</ref>。夾帶著良好的限映票房，本片在第三週擴展到全國上映，共在1,255間影院上映，以540萬美元的票房登上第六名<ref>{{Cite web |last=Subers |first=Ray |date=2015-04-26 |title=Weekend Report: 'Avengers' Opens to $201 Million Overseas |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/article/ed1048511492/ |website=Box Office Mojo |access-date=2022-06-17 |language=en |archive-date=2022-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220220065258/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/article/ed1048511492/ }}</ref>。第四個週末，本片受到強片影響，票房較上周下降58%，進帳220萬美元，排名第七<ref>{{Cite web |last=Subers |first=Ray |date=2015-05-03 |title=Weekend Report: 'Ultron's Massive $188M Debut Falls Short of 'Avengers' Record |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/article/ed1031734276/ |website=Box Office Mojo |access-date=2022-06-19 |language=en |archive-date=2022-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220530143757/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/article/ed1031734276/ }}</ref>。

